{"tid":966503,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"［問HR］一個位幾耐請唔到人先會raise budget?","createTime":"2019-01-03T00:21:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-03T05:50:10.000Z","uid":28526,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"1eceb207d941673eaea5f1edcccb378d4a1844ef","tid":966503,"uid":28526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:21:35.000Z","msg":"認真問<br />\n<br />\n如果有個位要求 min 3年經驗<br />\n但人工唔過20k<br />\n請人請左3個月都請唔到<br />\n<br />\n1. 收唔到cv，好少人申請<br />\n2. 見左幾個都唔岩<br />\n3. 約左幾個都冇出現<br />\n<br />\nProvided that<br />\n間公司係真係要請人而唔係假請人<br />\n無內定人選<br />\n<br />\n呢啲情況下<br />\n1. 一般公司幾耐先會考慮raise budget黎請人呢？<br />\n2. 如果2018年因為budget原因比唔到高價，一般公司會唔會在新一年度撥多啲$去請人？<br />\n<br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"9039b7a27de854a9b4bd4dcf740020093758ffbf","tid":966503,"uid":55969,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"725f2622d3fc8955da7cfd3a414e5c106a99fb5c","tid":966503,"uid":54617,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:25:51.000Z","msg":"香港公司諗法: <br />\n幾個月請唔到人都未執，即係唔請都得<br />\n班現職開OT死掂佢啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01c5d5acb6ba128f573d0b4ab9bbaa19bc1d6a89","tid":966503,"uid":29689,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:28:17.000Z","msg":"當公司做緊野嗰個等唔緊辭埋職嘅時候咪raise 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你係咪就係嗰個係公司做到死死下都未等到公司請人嘅心急人丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你一日唔辭職都唔會raise 喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99aee5fec5a0a38fa6dcacfcead195b304c33611","tid":966503,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:29:37.000Z","msg":"而家fg閒閒地都多過15啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b8fdc195ed51d96aaad7730b5a29752e44b1e5","tid":966503,"uid":61398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:31:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cfe154c479b163f3c3436a7968bdaffe20c2737b","tid":966503,"uid":28526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:40:03.000Z","msg":"我唔係做到死果個<br />\n係想fill 呢個位果個<br />\n所以想知道情況<br />\n<br />\n3年經驗20k唔夠<br />\n我初頭都唔信<br />\n後來我從現職朋友口中得知<br />\n因為價唔岩所以無得見<br />\n<br />\n我唔知jobdb/ctgood jobs果啲網點樣set job ad<br />\n佢個salary range set 15-30k<br />\nExp 3-8年<br />\n<br />\n我初頭以為我set within salary range+exp range就岩<br />\n原來佢公司2樣野都係set 最bottom 果個位<br />\n<br />\n即係原來佢只比到15-20k<br />\n<br />\n所以，係咪15-20k，3-8年經驗<br />\n呢2個option係job ad req field 入面<br />\nMust fill in option的最低果個選項？"},{"pid":"11aa0ac551ff9bc676c7d2a47f5d5e8509055657","tid":966503,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:40:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0679bcc6609d1d036612653ac7b161fbff697552","tid":966503,"uid":61018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9039b7a27de854a9b4bd4dcf740020093758ffbf","tid":966503,"uid":55969,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"quote":{"pid":"1eceb207d941673eaea5f1edcccb378d4a1844ef","tid":966503,"uid":28526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:21:35.000Z","msg":"認真問<br />\n<br />\n如果有個位要求 min 3年經驗<br />\n但人工唔過20k<br />\n請人請左3個月都請唔到<br />\n<br />\n1. 收唔到cv，好少人申請<br />\n2. 見左幾個都唔岩<br />\n3. 約左幾個都冇出現<br />\n<br />\nProvided that<br />\n間公司係真係要請人而唔係假請人<br />\n無內定人選<br />\n<br />\n呢啲情況下<br />\n1. 一般公司幾耐先會考慮raise budget黎請人呢？<br />\n2. 如果2018年因為budget原因比唔到高價，一般公司會唔會在新一年度撥多啲$去請人？<br />\n<br />\nThanks"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:24:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T01:04:59.000Z","msg":"搵agent算㗎啦<br />\n之後啲agent又西口西面"},{"pid":"bf3294e1eed190bf916e2966110811e854017fe2","tid":966503,"uid":28526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11aa0ac551ff9bc676c7d2a47f5d5e8509055657","tid":966503,"uid":131120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T00:40:04.000Z","msg"